#Spitch NdinguMphura. Kunale guy ndakhe ndadibana nayo ngo2012 kodwa sincokola njee singazange satsiba ziko kuba ndandisoyika kuba wayetshatile, okwesibini, indlela endandibona ngayo yayingathi ngumntu ofuna isilalo kum engabonakalisi thando ngoba wayesoloko endincoma ukumila kakuhle. Wandincekelela lo mfana ukusukela ngo2012 de yangu2018 efuna sidibane, kodwa  kwade kwenzeka ngo2019 sadibana, ndayolala kwakhe phofu, ndivume ngos’ke ndive ngo2016 ukuba inkosikazi yakhe yaye yasweleka. Kodwa ngoku sendilele naye khange ndibone mahluko kwindlela ebeyiyo nangona ukuqala kwam uyokulala kwakhe kulo nyaka ngoJanuary wathi emva kokuba waswelekelwa ngumfazi wakhe akana-stable relationship. Emva kokuba sendisukolala kwakhe waqala ngoku wanomntu, xa ndimfaka imibuzo wathi yena ewe, akangumntu onento ezinzileyo kodwa akathi akukho mntu ebomini bakhe. Waqala wandidika ke ngoku umntu xa ndileli kwakhe, okokuqala wandixelela ukuba bashiyana nge21yrs njengokuba mna endishiya nge10yrs. Waqhubekeka emane esithi intombi inyanisekile kuye wandiqwela ngenye emini esithi ugirl ngabantwana, caba wenza kwanto efunwa ngubhuti ebhedini. Mna ke andenzi nto endingekho comfortable ngayo, ewe ndiyenza kodwa endingekho comfortable for uyenza andivumi. Lo mfana sijola okanye undithatha xa kufuna yena mhlawumbi kanye ngenyanga . Ke mna Spitch ndingaba bantu bathetha phandle xa ndingayithandi into emntwini, andimthuki qha ndingumntu othethayo, yenye yezinto ebezingasivanisi ixesha elininzi mna naye. Ngenye imini ndimenzele voice note ndithethe yonke le nto endingayithandiyo kuye nendlela andiqhuba ngayo kuba enye into endiyiqapheleyo kulo mfana asikho bayi2 kuye ngendlela awatsho ngayo kum. Wandiphendula wathi yena lo mfana kum ‘ yena ebecinga sikwi-open relationship kuba mna ndandisoloko ndisenza iexcuse yongafuni udibana naye ndathi ndinomntu. 2 Wathi akekho ready ukuba kwirelationship nam. Kwezinye iimpendulo zakhe wayecela uxolo ngayo yonke into. Kwaye xa ndithethela uburongo bakhe wayesoloko qho esitsho ukuba yena emva kokuswelekelwa ngumfazi akasakhathali kwaye xa ndimamela indlela athetha ngayo ayindim ndodwa okhalazayo ngendlela ayiyo. Esithi inoba unengxaki yena oko waswelekelwa ngumfazi, uyababhekelisa abantu abasondeleyo ebomini bakhe. Ndaye ndamlahla ke mna kuba ndakhutyekiswa yindlela awandiphendula ngayo kwivoice note yam, asaphinda sathetha kwaphela iinyanga ezimbini. Kwiveki ephelileyo, gqi umntu endibulisa, endithethisa apha kuWhatsapp, sisathetha ke nangoku andiyaz ndithini Spitch kuba akancami, mna ndiyamthanda nangona ndingaboni thando kwelakhe icala.
